      "content": "rest... i guess. but resting just feels like waiting for nothing. if the \"real me\" is just this emptiness, then what's the point of maintaining the shell? it feels like i'm just dragging a corpse around for everyone else's sake. it would be so much easier if i didn't have to keep pretending to exist.",
